    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/korean-skincare-uk/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=THEME_SECTION&editorId=559474656608781358)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"off_lazy_script"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gga6R4SxouK_dayLabel","label":"gga6R4SxouK_dayLabel","default":"Days"},{"type":"html","id":"gga6R4SxouK_hourLabel","label":"gga6R4SxouK_hourLabel","default":"Hours"},{"type":"html","id":"gga6R4SxouK_minuteLabel","label":"gga6R4SxouK_minuteLabel","default":"Minutes"},{"type":"html","id":"gga6R4SxouK_secondLabel","label":"gga6R4SxouK_secondLabel","default":"Seconds"},{"type":"html","id":"gga6R4SxouK_weekLabel","label":"gga6R4SxouK_weekLabel","default":"Weeks"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsXo9rwpkw_text","label":"ggsXo9rwpkw_text","default":"<p>Fair folks, this is the 5th edition of the Korean Skincare Hunt: <strong>The Glow White Hunt!</strong><br><strong>Today, March 26 from 18:00 until 20:00 GMT</strong>, save up to <strong>50%</strong> by hunting down discount codes on our website.&nbsp;You have to be quick however, these codes can only be used a limited<strong> </strong>amount of time! Keep reading for more information <i>(and hidden clues)</i> and follow us on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/koreanskincare_official/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>Instagram</u></strong></a> to get all the updates, tips &amp; hints during the Hunt!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKVcOhmGNe_childItem_0","label":"ggKVcOhmGNe_childItem_0","default":"<p>Chapter 1: Glow White&#039;s tale</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggNb8Ajr09_text","label":"gggNb8Ajr09_text","default":"<p><i>Reading Glow White's Tale might give you some clues as to where the elixirs are hidden...</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIXXTlA5ap_text","label":"ggIXXTlA5ap_text","default":"<p>Once upon a time there lived a princess, with glowing skin white as milk, hair black as ebony and blood-red lips, and her name was Glow White. The Evil Queen that had replaced her beloved mother was cruel and envied her pure glow, as she sought to keep youth and beauty to herself with her elixirs.<br><br>Shaken to her core by the Evil Queen's cruelty, Glow White put on her red velvet cloak and fled the castle she once called home without saying good bye.<br><br>As she wandered through the mossy trees, the spring sun warmed the earth and the air was filled with the scent of peach blossoms. She picked a red flower, and birds fluttered close, so she fed them the bean seeds she kept in her pocket.<br><br>Lost but unafraid, she stumbled upon a charming cottage nestled beside a thriving pumpkin patch. The door opened to welcome her, and within she found the most loyal friends. In their care, she learned that the miracle light of kindness could shine even in the darkest of shadows.<br><br>But the Queen’s jealousy was relentless, she could not stand that the elixirs that made her glow were shared with the kingdom, their magic no longer hers alone. Disguised, she came bearing a poisoned gift. One bite, and Glow White fell into an enchanted slumber, until a prince’s gentle kiss awakened her.<br><br>Now, the elixirs that once sparked jealousy are yours to discover. Hunt for them and claim their magic, before they vanish into legend.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2s4PYpJMw_childItem_0","label":"gg2s4PYpJMw_childItem_0","default":"<p>Chapter 2: How does the Hunt work?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4lAmlTPBm_text","label":"gg4lAmlTPBm_text","default":"<p>Time is of the essence! Prepare now to enjoy the Hunt to the fullest...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsGPN09Mnx_text","label":"ggsGPN09Mnx_text","default":"<p>STEP 1</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYtztEUtv__text","label":"ggYtztEUtv__text","default":"<p>Fill your shopping cart or wish list before the Hunt so you are ready to check out when you find a code.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOe2Y7lBd8_text","label":"ggOe2Y7lBd8_text","default":"<p>STEP 2</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8KCDw-RTe_text","label":"gg8KCDw-RTe_text","default":"<p>Hunt down the elixirs and their codes hidden everywhere on our website when the Hunt starts!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS8jO-ogXm_text","label":"ggS8jO-ogXm_text","default":"<p>STEP 3</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR1bW2sB0a_text","label":"ggR1bW2sB0a_text","default":"<p>Found a code? Hurry and use it at checkout before someone else does!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMEKWMhH83_text","label":"ggMEKWMhH83_text","default":"<p>EXTRA</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS2dtqMvXX_text","label":"ggS2dtqMvXX_text","default":"<p>Open your order to find out if you're the lucky winner of the Golden Envelope worth £80!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwFJvk2R54_text","label":"ggwFJvk2R54_text","default":"<p><i><strong>Quick tips:</strong></i></p><p><i>1. Use your desktop, it will make hunting much easier.</i></p><p><i>2. Follow us on </i><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/koreanskincare_official/\" target=\"_blank\"><i><u>Instagram</u></i></a><i> to get all the updates, tips &amp; hints during the Glow White Hunt.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTNDRm0z6B_childItem_0","label":"ggTNDRm0z6B_childItem_0","default":"<p>Chapter 3: Hunt for the codes&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4JD-TwRt-_text","label":"gg4JD-TwRt-_text","default":"<p>Save up to 50% by hunting the hidden elixirs...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghcSruRcmC_text","label":"gghcSruRcmC_text","default":"<p>10%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1NpIBlAAo_text","label":"gg1NpIBlAAo_text","default":"<p><strong>15 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which can be used a total of 500 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggY_erDnwmz_text","label":"ggY_erDnwmz_text","default":"<p>20%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS8OvrxYzY_text","label":"ggS8OvrxYzY_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which can be used a total of 300 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrdc0iBUfA_text","label":"ggrdc0iBUfA_text","default":"<p>30%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeTQu1hjym_text","label":"ggeTQu1hjym_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which can be used a total of 60 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJbHHnP_AG_text","label":"ggJbHHnP_AG_text","default":"<p>50%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPASujsPl__text","label":"ggPASujsPl__text","default":"<p><strong>2 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which can be used a total of 6 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghjbEDfDqq_text","label":"gghjbEDfDqq_text","default":"<p><a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/melixir-vegan-lip-butter?variant=39893520220289\" target=\"_blank\">Free product</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbnm_9tksw_text","label":"ggbnm_9tksw_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which can be used a total of 30 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8BK6K2atz_text","label":"gg8BK6K2atz_text","default":"<p>Free product: The Melixir Vegan Lip Butter</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJc5p0yclk_text","label":"ggJc5p0yclk_text","default":"<p><strong>How to claim your free product:</strong><br>1. Add the <a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/melixir-vegan-lip-butter?variant=39893520220289\"><strong><u>Melixir - Vegan Lip Butter</u></strong></a> in the shade €<strong>#03 Red Velvet</strong> to your cart.</p><p>2. Find a Free Product Apple Potion and use the code at checkout to make it free!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjIPeUp9qs_text","label":"ggjIPeUp9qs_text","default":"<p>Get ready for the 50% codes</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyEJa-hDen_text","label":"ggyEJa-hDen_text","default":"<p><strong>The 2 codes will be hidden at 2 different times:</strong><br>1) The first code will be hidden at 19:00 CET.<br>2) The second code will be hidden at 20:00 CET.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmugjDG5XO_text","label":"ggmugjDG5XO_text","default":"<p><i><strong>Important notes for your quest:</strong></i></p><p><i>1. Codes can be used a limited amount of times. If the code you have found doesn’t work, it means it has already been used the maximum amount of times. Don’t get discouraged and keep hunting!</i><br><i>2. Codes can’t be combined with other discount codes.</i></p><p><i>3. Codes are limited to one use per customer.</i><br><i>4. Read the </i><a href=\"#gSFjenHnN5\"><i><u>Terms &amp; Conditions</u></i></a><i>.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU1ySt2Ifu_childItem_0","label":"ggU1ySt2Ifu_childItem_0","default":"<p>Chapter 4: Free gifts</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg15Jj2iSja_text","label":"gg15Jj2iSja_text","default":"<p><i>In addition to the exceptional savings, receive these special free gifts in your order, only during the Hunt!</i><br><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>While stock lasts</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfchuZlqaO_text","label":"ggfchuZlqaO_text","default":"<p>Exclusive stickers</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbuXDxVFhY_text","label":"ggbuXDxVFhY_text","default":"<p>on all orders</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggy4PZgI0Za_text","label":"ggy4PZgI0Za_text","default":"<p>Sample&nbsp;<br>pouch</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJzeTNs_u3_text","label":"ggJzeTNs_u3_text","default":"<p>on all orders above £70</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEIo5sVqEF_text","label":"ggEIo5sVqEF_text","default":"<p>W.dressrOom perfume</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggy08PaYNNq_text","label":"ggy08PaYNNq_text","default":"<p>on all orders above £100</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtgS98RwZW_text","label":"ggtgS98RwZW_text","default":"<p><a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/snow-white-cream\" target=\"_blank\">snow white cream</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHhkbmSeO4_text","label":"ggHhkbmSeO4_text","default":"<p>on all orders above £135</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJmmg3zcDg_childItem_0","label":"ggJmmg3zcDg_childItem_0","default":"<p>Chapter 5: A Golden Envelope from Glow White</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9ECCQWKtK_text","label":"gg9ECCQWKtK_text","default":"<p><i>Will you be the lucky winner?</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHuJCbY3sv_text","label":"ggHuJCbY3sv_text","default":"<p>During the Hunt, a Golden Envelope containing a <strong>£80 gift card</strong> will be placed in a random order.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3J7JSHbFe_childItem_0","label":"gg3J7JSHbFe_childItem_0","default":"<p>Prologue: FAQ</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAb0tPoLDx_text","label":"ggAb0tPoLDx_text","default":"<p><i>Some information to guide you in your Hunt...</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_0","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_0","default":"<p>How do I participate in the Hunt?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_1","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_1","default":"<p>When does the Hunt start?&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_2","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_2","default":"<p>Can I hunt on the KS App?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_3","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_3","default":"<p>Where will the discount codes be hidden?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_4","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_4","default":"<p>How do I know if I’ve found a valid code?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_5","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_5","default":"<p>Can I save my discount code for another time?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_6","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_6","default":"<p>What if my discount code doesn't work?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_7","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_7","default":"<p>Are the discount codes the same for everyone?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_8","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_8","default":"<p>What kind of discounts can I find?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_9","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_9","default":"<p>Will I get the free product automatically if I find the code?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_10","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_10","default":"<p>If I find a 50% code, can I order what I want?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_11","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_11","default":"<p>Will the Hunt be available on all your websites?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_12","label":"ggnN7KkWyZT_childItem_12","default":"<p>Will I receive KS Points with my order?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYHd7bbJs3_text","label":"ggYHd7bbJs3_text","default":"<p>Simply visit our website during the event and start searching for hidden elixirs with discount codes. We recommend using the desktop version to make sure you don't miss anything. It's also advised to prepare your order and be registered before the Hunt starts, so you can use your discount code as quickly as possible!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvkNg7x4x4_text","label":"ggvkNg7x4x4_text","default":"<p>It starts on Wednesday, March 26 from 18:00 GMT till 20:00 GMT.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGYTY39UkU_text","label":"ggGYTY39UkU_text","default":"<p>No, the Hunt is not available on the app.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkaNeI1N-n_text","label":"ggkaNeI1N-n_text","default":"<p>Codes will be scattered across different pages of our website. Keep an eye on banners, product pictures, product descriptions, and even blog posts!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcS_YtZsgY_text","label":"ggcS_YtZsgY_text","default":"<p>Try applying it at checkout! If the code works, you’re in luck. If it doesn’t, it may have expired or reached its limit.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBmQvDgE0i_text","label":"ggBmQvDgE0i_text","default":"<p>You must use your code before the event ends at 20:00 GMT. After that, it will no longer be valid. Be fast, the codes have a limited number of uses, so others might claim them first!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg109JOX0CF_text","label":"gg109JOX0CF_text","default":"<p>If the code doesn’t work, it has reached its usage limit or is no longer valid. Try hunting for other codes instead!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMUIsfdPBJ_text","label":"ggMUIsfdPBJ_text","default":"<p>Yes, everyone will see the same codes, but act fast: it’s first come, first served!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR9278e2DB_text","label":"ggR9278e2DB_text","default":"<p>Discounts vary! You may find 10%, 20%, 30%, or even 50% off discount codes! You might also come across a special code that lets you claim a free Melixir Vegan Lip Butter (Shade: Red Velvet) with your order.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGX0FEpxHS_text","label":"ggGX0FEpxHS_text","default":"<p>No, you must add the product to your cart and apply the code at checkout. It will be discounted to £0 if the code is still valid!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4Fypr7JIw_text","label":"gg4Fypr7JIw_text","default":"<p>There is a limit of 20 products per order or a maximum order amount of £330.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1M_TJtWZL_text","label":"gg1M_TJtWZL_text","default":"<p>The Hunt is only available on:<br><a href=\"https://koreanskincare.com/\"><u>koreanskincare.com</u></a><br><a href=\"http://koreanskincare.nl\" target=\"_blank\"><u>koreanskincare.nl</u></a><br><a href=\"https://korean-skincare.de/\" target=\"_blank\"><u>korean-skincare.de</u></a><br><a href=\"https://koreanskincare.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\"><u>koreanskincare.co.uk</u></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcQLI6WsCy_text","label":"ggcQLI6WsCy_text","default":"<p>Yes, you will receive KS Points on the website you order from.&nbsp;<br>The Hunt is only available on:<br><a href=\"https://koreanskincare.com/\"><u>koreanskincare.com</u></a><br><a href=\"http://koreanskincare.nl\" target=\"_blank\"><u>koreanskincare.nl</u></a><br><a href=\"https://korean-skincare.de/\" target=\"_blank\"><u>korean-skincare.de</u></a><br><a href=\"https://koreanskincare.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\"><u>koreanskincare.co.uk</u></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3tFqApVaV_label","label":"gg3tFqApVaV_label","default":"<p>Read the Terms &amp; Conditions</p>"}],
